Step 1: Lined
Begin by placing your hands at your underarms.
Work your way down the breast and back up again.
Repeat until you have got to the other side of your breast.

Step 2: Circular
Begin by placing your hands at the outer side of your breast.
Moving in a circular direction, continue until you reach your nipple.

Step 3: Radial
Start at the outer side of your breast.
Move your fingers towards your nipple and when you get there, return to your original position.
Move your fingers slightly to the side and repeat.
Continue until you cover the entire breast.




